This is a time lapse of the
camera being built, so a time

00:10:29.030 --> 00:10:31.100
lapse of the time lapse.

00:10:31.100 --> 00:10:34.840
But this is something that was
founded in his garage.

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:38.050
He had random parts from the
hardware store that he put

00:10:38.050 --> 00:10:40.110
together, and he built something
that he thought

00:10:40.110 --> 00:10:43.110
could be installed and would,
hopefully, last for a long

00:10:43.110 --> 00:10:44.640
period of time.

