And the first trip that
we did to Iceland--

00:10:47.380 --> 00:10:49.650
it was in March of 2007--

00:10:49.650 --> 00:10:53.350
it was a team of these six guys,
and we had the cameras

00:10:53.350 --> 00:10:54.960
that James had designed
out in the field.

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:56.690
And we got to Iceland.

00:10:56.690 --> 00:10:57.810
We had these tripods.

00:10:57.810 --> 00:10:59.170
We were going to mount
them to the ground.

00:10:59.170 --> 00:11:01.520
